headline.main: SWISS HERE DOUBT TIGHTER BLOCKADE; No Notice of British Threat Received in Official Circles

lead_paragraph: Doubt was expressed in official Swiss quarters here last week that Great Britain intended to tighten her blockade of Switzerland, as reported from London the previous week.
abstract: Brit tightening of blockade against Switzerland doubted in Swiss qrs, N Y C
